        "text": [
          "ه عن زياد بن سوقة فقد رويته عن أبي- رضي اللّه عنه- عن سعد ابن عبد اللّه، عن أيّوب بن نوح، عن محمّد بن أبي عمير، عن زياد بن سوقة."
        ],
        "translations": {
          "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
            "Everything in this book that is narrated from Ziyad ibn Suwqah has been transmitted by me from my father - may Allah (swt) be pleased with him - from Sa'd ibn Abdullah, from Ayyub ibn Nuh, from Muhammad ibn Abi 'Umayr, from Ziyad ibn Suwqah."
